 "remarks": "28 Bulkley Avenue North offers a rare furnished or unfurnished lease opportunity in Westport, Connecticut 06880, just one light to the Greens Farms train station for an easy commute to Grand Central Terminal. This beautifully renovated 1799 antique Colonial blends historic charm with modern luxury on a flat, half-acre lot. Spanning 5,793 square feet, the home offers five bedrooms, three full baths, and two half baths, with six fireplaces bringing warmth and character throughout. The chef&apos;s kitchen features a Sub-Zero refrigerator, a Wolf range, custom cabinetry, and generous prep space opening to a sun-filled family room. The primary suite includes an oversized dressing room and a spa-like bath with a soaking tub and steam shower. The finished lower level adds a game room, wine cellar, and flexible recreation space. For a 12-to-16-month lease at $14,000 per month furnished or $12,000 per month unfurnished.  Minutes to Long Lots Elementary, Post Road shopping, and Main Street dining. A rare lease opportunity blending antique charm and modern living in Westport, CT 06880.",
